  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA91">
<l>tiraimaruvu ceñcaṭaiyāṉ cēvaṭikkē yāḷā</l>
<l>yuraimaruvi yāmuṇarntōṅ kaṇṭīr - terimiṉō</l>
<l>vimmaikku mammaikku mellā mamaintōmē</l>
<l>yemmaip puṟamuraippa teṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being servants to the red feet of him with red matted hair joined by waves</l>
<l>we have adopted [and] understood [his] word, see. Be clear [about this]:</l>
<l>Us who are suited to this birth and the other,</l>
<l>why slander us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
